                                    <div class="flex md:justify-end items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-trophy text-yellow-500 text-xs"></i><span>Champion: <strong class="text-white">Lake Champlain Champs</strong></span></div>
                                    <div class="flex md:justify-end items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-certificate text-yellow-600 text-xs"></i><span>Gold Jacket · Dylan (Vermont)</span></div>
                                    <div class="flex md:justify-end items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-users text-gray-500 text-xs"></i><span>12 OG Founding Teams</span></div>
                                    <div class="flex md:justify-end items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket text-blue-400 text-xs"></i><span>First season of the 1st Dynasty</span></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center z-10 relative">
                            <div class="timeline-node ring-2 ring-[#D4AF37]/30"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
                            <div class="glass rounded-xl p-4 text-xs text-gray-500 mono space-y-1">
                                <p class="text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest mb-2">Notable Events</p>
                                <p>· League founded by Commissioner Dan Frank</p>
                                <p>· 12-team Top Level only</p>
                                <p>· Snake startup draft</p>
                                <p>· Constitution Rev 2023.1 ratified</p>
