                                    <div class="flex md:justify-end items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-trophy text-yellow-500 text-xs"></i><span>Champion: <strong class="text-white">Southie Thunder Buddies</strong></span></div>
                                    <div class="flex md:justify-end items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-certificate text-yellow-500 text-xs"></i><span>Green Jacket · Dan (Massachusetts)</span></div>
